^-|CP||FP||at|^B@2^Z@3Bridge information stays with me as long as writing on the sand at the beach. It takes only one soft wave to wash everything away. However, as I get older I become more persistent and keep writing on the sand--reviewing the material over and over. This week I have a gem from "The Latest Bridge Base Online News" and an important announcement. First the gem.|
PG| ***** 95 ***** |


NT||
