^-|CP||FP||at|^B@2^Z@32. Counting High Card Points
Count high cards from left to right, keeping a running total. Then count again, counting from right to left. Or count by pairing up lower honors into units of 4 HCP (KJ, QQ) then adding four for each ace, four for each pair and finally counting any unpaired lower honors. It does not really matter. Just count multiple times using different approaches to catch errors. |
