^-|CP||FP||at|^B@2^Z@32. Use mental tricks to restore your equilibrium after a strong emotion:
A. Take several deep breaths.
B. Count to ten.
C. Imagine a place that reminds you of happy feelings.
D. Repeat a calming phrase over and over.|
